name: 結華
text: まみみん！　次の仕事、二人だねぇ
trans: Mamimin! Our next job is just us two, huh?

name: 摩美々
text:
そーみたいだねー
まぁ、よろしくー
trans:
Looks like it.
Well, let's do our beeest.

name: 結華
text:
よろしくー
ちなみに番組のこと、何か聞いてる？
trans:
Likewise! By the way...
You heard what we'll be doing in the show, right?

name: 摩美々
text:
んー？　何かあったっけー
ってなんか三峰うれしそー？
trans:
Hmm? What about it?
You seem really happy about it, Mitsumine.

name: 結華
text:
あはー、やっぱわかっちゃう？
だってその仕事、私服で出てって言われたからさ！
trans:
Yup! Haven't you heard?
We'll be able to wear our own clothes at the job!

name: 結華
text: 人気のファッション番組だし、今から楽しみで！
trans: It's a popular fashion show, so I'm pretty psyched!

name: 摩美々
text:
あー、そーいえばぁ……
新鮮だとは思うケド……それ以上にめんどーかもー
trans:
Uh, come to think of it... I was thinking of going in a
flashy outfit for the show... But it sounds like a pain.

name: 結華
text: えーっ、なんで？　どこが！？
trans: Ehhh, why? What part bothers you?

name: 摩美々
text:
私服ってところー
新鮮だけどめんどーかなぁ
trans:
The part where we wear our own clothes.
Dressing up all flashy is too much of a pain, right?

name: 結華
text:
そんなこと言わずにさぁ
三峰、まみみんの服、攻めてて好きなんだよ
trans:
How can you say that?
Mitsumine really likes your fashion sense!

name: 結華
text:
一緒に楽しく私服で出よー？
まみみんのかっこいいとっておき、三峰に見せてー！
trans:
I want us to have fun together in style, you know?
You got something cool going on, and Mitsumine
wants you to show it off!

name: 摩美々
text:
そう言われてもー、
服とかたくさんあるから選ぶのも大変なんだよー？
trans:
Even if you say that, I have too many clothes, and
having to pick an outfit seems like a draaag.

name: 摩美々
text:
それに、衣装合わせのために
いっぱい持って来なきゃいけないのはもっとめんどー
trans:
Also in order to pick the best one, I'd have to bring all
of those clothes here, which is even mooore of a drag.

name: 結華
text:
あー……確かに、服持って事務所に
集合しなきゃなのは、ねぇ……
trans:
Huh, you're right about that...
We'd have to carry all of our clothes to the office...

name: 摩美々
text:
そうだよー？
荷物増えるだけだからねー
trans:
Riiight?
We'll just be overrun with luggage.

name: 結華
text:
……いや、でも待って！
これはむしろチャンスなんじゃないだろうか！
trans:
...No, wait a sec!
This could actually be a great opportunity!

name: 摩美々
text:
チャンスー？
どーゆーことー？
trans:
An opportunity?
What do you meeean?

name: 結華
text:
三峰さ、まみみんのこと、
一度コーディネートしてみたいと思ってたんだよね
trans:
An opportunity for this Mitsumine to be your
personal coordinator for the day, Mamimin!

name: 摩美々
text:
私をー？
三峰、そんなこと考えてたんだねー
trans:
For meee? That's something only you can come up
with, Mitsumine.

name: 結華
text:
そう！　だから、たとえ荷物が重くても、
着せ替えして遊ぶためだと思えば苦じゃないはず……！
trans:
Yep! So even if your luggage was heavy, it wouldn't be
too much trouble if you think that it's for changing
clothes and dressing up!

name: 結華
text:
三峰はこのチャンスをゲットしたい！
どうかな、まみみん！？
trans:
This is the chance Mitsumine wants to take!
What do you think, Mamimin?

name: 摩美々
text: 三峰が私をコーディネートかぁ……
trans: Mitsumine as my coordinator...

name: 摩美々
text: まぁ……それは面白そうかもー
trans: Well... I guess that kinda sounds like fun.

name: 結華
text: おっ、好感触！　いいよいいよまみみん！
trans: Oh! An agreement! Good to hear, Mamimin!

name: 摩美々
text:
ちょっと興味出たかもー
……私も私でー……
trans:
There's something on my mind though...
It's just that I...

name: 結華
text: ん？　あれどしたの？　やっぱやめるとかそういう？！
trans:
Hmm? What is it?
Don't tell me you want to back out already?!

name: 摩美々
text:
ふふー
チャンスっていえば、私もそうかもーって思ったんだぁ
trans:
Fufu...
I also think it's a good opportunity.

name: 摩美々
text: ……実は前から三峰の服、気になってたんだよねー
trans:
I've been really interested in your clothes for a while
now, Mitsumine.

name: 摩美々
text:
服のセンスとかぁ、合わせとかぁ
けっこー見てたりするんだよー？
trans:
Your fashion sense and your outfits are something
I'd like to try out for myself.

name: 結華
text:
おおっ、ほんとに？
三峰のファッションに興味あったりする？
trans:
Woah! Really?
You're really interested in Mitsumine's style?

name: 摩美々
text: そうかもー
trans: Yeah.

name: 摩美々
text:
三峰って個性的な格好が多いからぁ、
けっこー私と服のセンス近いと思っててー
trans:
You've perfected many unique outfits.
Your fashion sense isn't that far off from mine either.

name: 摩美々
text:
だから三峰がどーゆー服持ってくるのか、
ちょっと気にはなるかなぁ
trans:
That's why I'm curious on what you'll be bringing,
Mitsumine.

name: 結華
text:
なるほど、だったらなおさらラッキーなんじゃない？
まみみん、三峰の服見放題だよ
trans:
I see. Aren't you a lucky one?
I'll even let you look around as much as you want!

name: 結華
text:
……あ、そうだ。ここまできたらさぁ、
まみみんも三峰の服、コーディネートしてよ！
trans:
...Ah, okay. Since we're going all the way here...
...You can coordinate for Mitsumine too!

name: 摩美々
text: 私も三峰の服、選んでいいってことー？
trans: You're okay with me picking yooour clothes?

name: 結華
text:
そうそう！
まみみんは三峰の！　三峰はまみみんの！
trans:
You bet!
Mamimin will do Mitsumine's!
And Mitsumine will do Mamimin's!

name: 結華
text:
お互いのセンスで、お互いに着せたい服を選んだら
面白そうじゃない？
trans:
Wouldn't it be interesting to see how we'll look
after we dress each other up?

name: 結華
text:
手持ちの服で、自分じゃ絶対思いつかないコーデが
見れたりするかもしれないし！
trans:
With the clothes we're bringing over, we might be
able to create new outfits for each other that we
wouldn't ever have thought of on our own!

name: 摩美々
text:
確かにおもしろそーだねー、
三峰のことコーディネートしてみたかったし、いいよー
trans:
It really doooes sound like fun if you  put that way.
I've been wanting to coordinate an outfit for you too.
Let's do it.

name: 摩美々
text: そしたら、私もちゃんと服持ってこなきゃだなぁ……
trans:
And I guess, this means I really have to think about
what to choose...

name: 摩美々
text:
三峰のおかげで、
ちょっとやる気でたかもー
trans:
Thanks to you, Mitsumine...
...I might even feel a bit motivated.

name: 摩美々
text:
私服持ってくるのはやっぱりめんどーだけどー
楽しみができたから頑張ろーかなぁ
trans:
Lugging all of my clothes is still a drag, but at least
you got me looking forward to something.
Maybe I really should put in more work.

name: 結華
text: やーった！　まみみん物分かりがいい！
trans: Woohoo! Mamimin's so understanding!

name: 摩美々
text: 三峰の服、楽しみにしてるからぁ
trans:
Mitsumine, I'm looking to your clothes
most of all.

name: 結華
text: 三峰もだよ、当日よろしくね
trans: Mitsumine too! I can't wait!

name: 摩美々
text:
ふふー
衣装合わせ、けっこー楽しみかもー
trans:
Fufu, I'm actually kinda looking forward to
picking out our outfits together.
